  "text": "We choose one realizationκ(x) = κ(x, ξ * ) as the reference diffusion coefficient andû(x, ξ * ), the corresponding solution of Eqs (30) and (31), as the reference hydraulic head. Finite volume method with uniform mesh (80 × 20 elements) is adopted to solve Eqs (30) and [CITATION_1] . We consider two sets ofκ observations, inlcuding a randomly sampledκ andκ sampled based on the expert knowledge of local maxima and minima ofκ. For each distribution ofκ measurements, we consider two sets ofû measurements, randomly located and chosen based on σ 2 u (x) as described in Section 5.1. The relative error ε in the estimatedκ are computed for each case using Eq (29).",
